  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Scandic is offered on a half-board basis with breakfast and dinner included in your stay. Drinks are not included.</p>
<p>Breakfast includes a hot and cold buffet spread. You'll have a range of items to choose from including freshly baked breads, yoghurts, cereals, fresh fruits, boiled and scrambled eggs, bacon and sausages.</p>
<p>Dinner consists of a 3-course buffet. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>1</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Located right by the train station, the Scandic is in a prime location and </span>offers stunning views of the surrounding mountains and lakes. The hotel has a cosy, Scandinavian style with comfortable rooms that make you feel right at home. With its friendly atmosphere, Scandic Voss is a fantastic base for if you're looking to experience the best of Western Norway.</p>
<h2><span>Wellness facilities</span></h2>
<p><span>During your stay in Hotel Scandic, you'll have access to both a gym and a sauna. For those active individuals, you can visit the gym before hitting the slopes to warm up those leg muscles. Then after an energetic day out in the snow, spend some time unwinding in the warmth of the sauna. Both the sauna and the gym have a terrace area with fantastic views of Lake Vangsvatnet.</span></p>
<h2><span>Haik bar and restaurant</span><span></span></h2>
<p><span>Following the seasons, the Haik restaurant's menu centres around a closed charcoal grill. All dishes are made with local and traditional Norwegian ingredients, so you'll have the opportunity to taste some of the finest dishes Norway has to offer. After your meal, head over to the Haik bar area where the talented bartenders provide a delicious range of drinks and snacks. Socialise with friends and take in the fantastic views of the resort and surrounding fjords, or challenge each other to a game of shuffleboard.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
